article.description: — Malik Miller posted 15 points as Morgan State defeated South Carolina State 77-63 on Monday night.
article.headline: Miller scores 15 to carry Morgan St. over SC State 77-63
article.linkText: Miller scores 15 to carry Morgan St. over SC State 77-63
article.story: BALTIMORE -- — Malik Miller posted 15 points as Morgan State defeated South Carolina State 77-63 on Monday night. Troy Baxter had 16 points for Morgan State (8-9, 2-0 Mid-Eastern Athletic Conference). Stanley Davis added 14 points and six rebounds and Sherwyn Devonish had 11 points and six assists. Morgan State posted a season-high 20 assists. Damani Applewhite had 17 points and seven rebounds for the Bulldogs (6-8, 1-1). Tashombe Riley added 12 points and Ian Kinard had 10 points and seven rebounds. Morgan State takes on Florida A&M on the road on Saturday. South Carolina State plays Howard on the road next Monday.
